# Cursor rules

Project-specific agent instructions live in **`.cursor/rules/*.mdc`** (scoped by topic).

Reference docs (this repo):

- `docs/project_structure.md` — module map, where to edit
- `docs/architecture.md` — UI/BFF flows and architectural decisions
- `docs/agent_api_contract.md` — outbound agent API + LiveKit contract

**Optional monorepo:** if a compatible agent API repo is open at `../personal-voice-agent`, read its `docs/` only when changing worker behaviour, LangGraph, or telephony — not for UI-only tasks.

Do not duplicate long architecture prose here.
